                    "subtype": "ability",
                    "ability_type": "automatic",
                    "name": "Top-Heavy",
                    "text": "A spiral centurion's top-like design makes it susceptible to effects that would cause it to fall prone. The DC of any attempt to knock the spiral centurion <a aonid=\"31\" game-obj=\"Conditions\">prone</a> is reduced by 5. If the spiral centurion attempts a check or saving throw to resist being knocked prone, it takes a -5 status penalty. A spiral centurion that has been knocked prone can-t use any actions other than to attempt to Stand, but it must succeed at a DC 30 <a aonid=\"1\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Acrobatics</a> check to do so."
                }
